article.headline: Sherfield, Coleman carry Nevada past North Dakota St. 62-48
article.linkText: Sherfield, Coleman carry Nevada past North Dakota St. 62-48
article.story: LINCOLN, Neb. -- — Grant Sherfield had 14 points as Nevada got past North Dakota State 62-48 on Wednesday at the Golden Window Classic. Tre Coleman had 13 points for Nevada (1-0). K.J. Hymes added 11 points. Robby Robinson had 10 rebounds. Tyree Eady had 11 points for the Bison (0-1). Rocky Kreuser added 10 rebounds. Tyler Witz had seven rebounds. ------ For more AP college basketball coverage: https://apnews.com/Collegebasketball and http://twitter.com/AP--Top25 ------ This was generated by Automated Insights, http://www.automatedinsights.com/ap, using data from STATS LLC, https://www.stats.com
